\par 
\par \hich\af319\dbch\af31505\loch\f319  unit of navy doctors at the plank; preschoolers, and early graders clutching
\par \hich\af319\dbch\af31505\loch\f319  ident\hich\af319\dbch\af31505\loch\f319 ical traveling kits and one another's hands, peering up at the strange
\par \hich\af319\dbch\af31505\loch\f319  black vessel that was to be their home for weeks to come.
\par \hich\af319\dbch\af31505\loch\f319   "Incredible," said theofficer. "Simply incredible."
\par \hich\af319\dbch\af31505\loch\f319   "It's the beginning," replied the man in the overcoat, his sharp,- ang\hich\af319\dbch\af31505\loch\f319 ular
\par \hich\af319\dbch\af31505\loch\f319   features rigid. "Word comes from everywhere. From the ports and the
\par \hich\af319\dbch\af31505\loch\f319   mountain passes, from the remaining airfields all over the Reich. They go
\par \hich\af319\dbch\af31505\loch\f319   out by the thousands. To every part of the world. And people are waiting
\par \hich\af319\dbch\af31505\loch\f319   for them. Everywhere."
\par \hich\af319\dbch\af31505\loch\f319   "An extraordinary accomplishmenV' said the officer, shaking his head in
\par \hich\af319\dbch\af31505\loch\f319   awe.
\par \hich\af319\dbch\af31505\loch\f319   *This is only one part of the strategy. The entire operation is
\par \hich\af319\dbch\af31505\loch\f319   extraordinary."
